description: Wesley Woods is anticipating BIG birthday plans once his boyfriend gets home. Wesley's hopes are quickly dashed when his boyfriend calls to say he can't make it home for Wesley's birthday. But then it only takes a knock on the door to change Wesley's mood from sullen to excited when Max Konnor is his surprise for the night! The two are ready to celebrate as Wesley unwraps his gift and is ready to ride the thick, rock-hard 'package' that is made for his tight holes to fill.
title: Birthday Surprise, Scene #01
